<head>TONE</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">音調</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>SOUND at a DEFINED PITCH as PART of a MUSICAL SYSTEM.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>音</p>
<p>first rough draft to identify synonym group members for future analysis, based on CL. 18.11.2003. CH</p>
        </div>
<div type="old-chinese-contrasts">
<p>CHANGDUANJING:</p>
<p>樂書曰：</p>
<p>知聲而不知音者，</p>
<p>禽獸是也。</p>
<p>知音而不知樂者，</p>
<p>眾庶是也。</p>
<p>唯君子為能知樂。</p>
<p>是故審聲以知音，</p>
<p>審音以知樂，</p>
<p>審樂以知正，</p>
<p>而理道備矣。</p>
<p>此又音聲之異也。）</p>
        </div>
